intros A B l ls f s1 s2 H1 H2.

Lemma bigcup_setI_cons_subset_r : forall (A B : Type) (l : A) (ls : seq A) (f : A -> set B) (s1 s2 : set B) (s3 : set A), s3 l -> s1 \subset f l -> s2 \subset \bigcup_(x in ls :&: s3) f x -> s1 :|: s2 \subset \bigcup_(x in (l :: ls) :&: s3) f x.
intros A B l ls f s1 s2 s3 H1 H2 H3.
Lemma imset_union_set_eq: forall (U T : Type) (s1 s2 : set U) (f : U -> T), f @: (s1 :|: s2) <--> f @: s1 :|: f @: s2.
intros U T s1 s2 f.

Lemma imset_bigcup_setI_cons_subset_r : forall (A B : Type) (l : A) (ls : seq A) (f : A -> set (option B)) (s1 s2 : set B) (s3 : set A), s3 l -> Some @: s1 \subset f l -> Some @: s2 \subset \bigcup_(x in ls :&: s3) f x -> Some @: (s1 :|: s2) \subset \bigcup_(x in (l :: ls) :&: s3) f x.
intros A B l ls f s1 s2 s3 H1 H2 H3.
Lemma imset_set0_subset {A B} (f : A -> B) (s : set B) : (f @: set0) \subset s.
Lemma setI_set_eq_r {A : Type} (s1 s2 s2' : set A) : s2 <--> s2' -> (s1 :&: s2) <--> (s1 :&: s2').
Lemma isSome_subset {A : Type} (s1 s2 s1' s2' : set (option A)) : isSome :&: s1 \subset isSome :&: s2 -> isSome :&: (s1 :|: ([set None] :&: s1')) \subset isSome :&: (s2 :|: ([set None] :&: s2')).
destruct x as [ x | ]; try discriminate.
Lemma bigcup_nil_setI {A B} (f : A -> set B) (l : seq A) s : \bigcup_(x in [] :&: s) (f x) \subset \bigcup_(x in (l :&: s)) (f x).
Lemma isSome_set_eq {A} (s : set (option A)) (s' : set A) : s \subset (Some @: s') :|: [set None] -> Some @: s' \subset s -> isSome :&: s <--> Some @: s'.
Lemma set_eq_isSome_sound {A} (s : set (option A)) (s' : set A) : isSome :&: s <--> Some @: s' -> s \subset (Some @: s') :|: [set None].
Lemma set_eq_isSome_complete {A} (s : set (option A)) (s' : set A) : isSome :&: s <--> Some @: s' -> Some @: s' \subset s.
Definition somes {A} (s : set (option A)) : set A := [set x | Some x \in s].
Lemma somes_subset {A} (s1 s2 : set (option A)) : s1 \subset s2 -> somes s1 \subset somes s2.
Lemma bigcup_somes {A B} (sA : set A) (s : A -> set (option B)) : somes (\bigcup_(a in sA) s a) <--> \bigcup_(a in sA) somes (s a).
intro b; split; intros [a Ha]; eexists a; auto.
Instance proper_somes A : Morphisms.Proper (set_eq ==> set_eq) (@somes A).
Lemma bigcup_setI {T U} (s1 : set T) (s2 : set U) F : \bigcup_(x in s1) (s2 :&: F x) <--> s2 :&: \bigcup_(x in s1) (F x).
